        </p>

        <!-- INTRO -->
        <section id="intro">
          <p>
            Knowing the time difference between countries is essential for
            scheduling meetings, coordinating work, booking travel, and staying
            connected with people around the world.
          </p>

          <p>
            While it may seem as simple as adding or subtracting hours, time
            difference calculation is affected by time zones, daylight saving
